data.description: Spacious well maintained home with 3 bedroom 2 bath home with fireplace in family room. 2 living areas, kitchen bar includes the wooden bar stools.  Separate dining area and additional formal area.  Laminate and ceramic tile flooring. RECENT UPGRADES:  Recently replaced roof, new cement back patio slab and extended back patio roof covering, outdoor ceiling fans, motion lights, New gutters on all sides of house, new ceiling fans in master bedroom & family room, new butcher block kitchen counter tops, new flooring in family rm, dining, hallway and master bedroom, new blinds in family room & master,  new duck work. Large lot with mature trees and covered back patio. Open floor plan with large multifunctional living space.  2 car garage.  Located near shopping, restaurants, schools, park, SeaWorld, lackland AFB,  No HOA.
